4 slice(s) Country Style Sliced Bread
2 sachet(s) Peanut Butter
100 grams Blueberry Jam

Spread peanut butter evenly over two of the bread slices.

Spread the blueberry jam evenly over the remaining bread slices.

Sandwich the bread slices with peanut butter onto the bread slices with jam.
Cut the sandwiches diagonally.